    "body": "I think the best way to do so is:\r\n```\r\nfrom, err := types.Sender(types.NewEIP155Signer(tx.ChainId()), tx) \r\nif err != nil {\r\n    from, err := types.Sender(types.HomesteadSigner{}, tx) \r\n}\r\n```\r\nOr you can use the ` types.LatestSignerForChainID(chainID *big.Int)` function to get the latest signer",
